## âš ï¸ **9. Important Facts About Management Groups**

| Rule                                  | Detail                                                             |
| ------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------ |
| **Max 10,000 management groups**      | per directory                                                      |
| **Max 6 levels deep**                 | excluding root/subscription                                        |
| **One parent only**                   | Each management group or subscription can have **only one parent** |
| **Inheritance applies automatically** | All policies/RBAC flow down the hierarchy                          |

